TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.UPC_CODE, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.SELLING_STYLE, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY, FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID FROM FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT,FCST_ITEM_SKU WHERE FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.FCST_SKU_KEY=FCST_ITEM_SKU.FCST_SKU_KEY AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID=FCST_ITEM_SKU.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID AND (FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.BUSINESS_SEG_HIERARCHY_ID = 5 OR FCST_ITEM_SKU.DIVISION_GROUP='sls') AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.PLACE_HOLDER NOT IN ('P','F') AND FCST_DEMAND_PRODUCT.PROCESS_IND='Y' AND FCST_ITEM_SKU.DIVISION_GROUP='sls'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
